Java - Command Line


>>>set CLASSPATH:
update:
set CLASSPATH=path1;path2;...

delete all:
set CLASSPATH=

check:
echo %CLASSPATH%

..either return the path(s) or return "%CLASSPATH%"


>>> run java class program with external jar file:

1. make sure 'java' is recognized as a command
in folder outside java path...

java -version

2. cd.. enter into xxx.class folder

3. java .;path/to/jarfile.jar xxx [String[] args]


